   Preferred Qualifications 




      A degree in Nursing; 
      Successful completion of a critical care program or consolidation in critical care; 
      Recent courses in coronary care, critical care; UoHI Cardiac Nursing Series; 
      Experience reading and interpreting 12 lead ECG's; 
      Member RNAO; 
      Member CCCN; 
      Proficiency in English and French – oral expression (advanced level) and comprehension (advanced level).







